# Per-developer MCP wiring — local dev runtime endpoint, ports vary.
.mcp.json
# Source/compiled split — `.skill.md` is the authored/committed source;
# `.skill` is the compiled artifact (prompt text emitted by compile), paired
# with `.skill.provenance.json`. Both compiled outputs are derived and
# regenerate from source on demand.
*.skill
!**/scaffold/**/*.skill
*.skill.provenance.json
*.provenance.json
# v0.4.0 — `connectors.json` is secret-bearing (env credentials live there
# alongside `${VAR}` references). Default-gitignored to prevent accidental
# commit. Use `connectors.json.example` as the version-controlled template.
# Root-anchored so the scaffold's bundled placeholder stays tracked.
/connectors.json
